{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__001", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "适用范围", "chunk_text": "本政策用于回答旅客关于航班改签、可改签条件、不可改签场景以及改签后关联服务是否保留的问题。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__002", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "可以在线改签的机票", "chunk_text": "符合以下条件的机票通常可以在线改签：\n\n- 机票号码以 `724` 开头。\n- 机票不是通过易货或代金券支付。\n- 如果机票通过代金券全额支付，部分情况下可能可以在线改签；具体以系统提示为准。\n- 机票必须有有效航班预订。\n- 当前支持单程票或单程航线的往返票，也就是点对点行程。\n- 改签内容限于航班和旅行日期。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__003", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "不能在线改签的机票或预订", "chunk_text": "以下情况通常不能在线改签：\n\n- 包含其他航空公司航段的预订。\n\n- 包含尚未出票的预订。\n\n- 同一旅客、同一路线下存在多张有效机票。\n\n- 机票状态不是开放状态。\n\n- 航段状态不是确认状态，例如候补状态。\n\n- 未显示票价计算的 IT 机票。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__004", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "不能在线改签的机票或预订", "chunk_text": "- 包含特殊服务的预订，例如动物运输、医疗设备运输、特殊运动器材运输等。\n\n- 团体预订中的机票。\n\n- 预订舱位与票价代码不一致的机票。\n\n- 在线兑换预订当前不能通过 swiss.com 改签。\n\n- 已在线办理登机手续的机票不能在线改签。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__005", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "可修改内容", "chunk_text": "在线改签通常支持修改：\n\n- 航班。\n- 旅行日期。\n\n在线改签通常不支持修改：\n\n- 出发地。\n- 目的地。\n- 旅客姓名。\n- 同一预订中的部分乘客。\n- 乘客人数。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__006", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "起飞前改签时间限制", "chunk_text": "在线改签的最短提前时间取决于出发机场。\n\n对于从瑞士机场出发的航班，通常可以在起飞前至少 3 小时进行在线改签。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__007", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "多次改签", "chunk_text": "如果票价条件允许，已改签后的行程可以再次改签。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__008", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "改签后的订单和服务影响", "chunk_text": "改签后，以下信息或服务通常会保留：\n\n- 原预订参考号保持不变。\n- 座位预订会包含在改签中。\n- 特殊餐食会包含在改签中。\n- 附加乘客信息 APIS 会包含在改签中。\n- 通过瑞士航空购买的欧洲旅行保险会包含在新机票中，并保持有效。\n\n改签后，旅客通常会获得新的机票号码。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__009", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "费用和货币", "chunk_text": "与改签相关的计算通常使用原始出发国家或起始点的货币。\n\n如果新航班更便宜，当前 FAQ 表述为机场税差额不会在线退还。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__010", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "旅行社和套餐预订", "chunk_text": "通过旅行社购买的航班预订可以在线更改，但旅行社可能无法访问新的电子机票。\n\n如果航班属于旅行社购买的套餐，在线改签通常只处理航班预订，不处理套餐中包含的酒店、租车等其他服务。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "ticket_change_policy__011", "policy_id": "ticket_change_policy", "title": "机票改签政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "change", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/ticket_change_policy.md", "section_title": "客服处理建议", "chunk_text": "Agent 在执行改签操作前应先：\n\n1. 查询当前乘客机票。\n2. 查询改签政策。\n3. 搜索候选航班。\n4. 向用户明确新航班、时间和可能影响。\n5. 获得用户确认后再执行改签。\n\n涉及特殊服务、团体预订、非开放状态机票、旅行社套餐或系统无法判断的场景，应升级人工处理。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__001", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "适用范围", "chunk_text": "本政策用于回答旅客关于取消航班、退款条件、退款渠道、退款货币以及不同票价退款差异的问题。", "risk_level": "medium", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__002", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "一般取消规则", "chunk_text": "旅客是否可以取消航班以及是否产生费用，取决于以下因素：\n\n- 票价类型。\n- 取消时间。\n- 原购买渠道。\n- 是否已经出票。\n- 是否已经办理值机。\n- 是否涉及团体、特殊服务或第三方行程。\n\n当前 FAQ 中存在一段疑似外部网页拼接的取消指南，包含电话号码和重复步骤。该段内容未直接纳入正式政策，仅保留其中需要人工确认的概念性信息。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__003", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "24 小时取消规则", "chunk_text": "原始 FAQ 的外部拼接段落提到：最灵活票价类型可能允许旅客在起飞前 24 小时取消航班且不支付罚金。\n\n待人工确认：\n\n- 24 小时取消规则是否适用于所有渠道。\n- 24 小时规则是“购票后 24 小时内”还是“起飞前 24 小时前”。\n- 哪些票价类型属于最灵活票价。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__004", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "24 小时取消规则", "chunk_text": "在未确认前，Agent 不应直接承诺免费取消。", "risk_level": "medium", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__005", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "不同票价类型的退款差异", "chunk_text": "当前 FAQ 表明：\n\n- 灵活类票价通常有更高的改退灵活性。\n- 非灵活经济舱票价取消时可能产生取消费用。\n- 取消时间越接近出发日期，取消费用可能越高。\n- 经济轻便票价中的第一件付费行李费用通常不予退还，也不能转用于其他航班。\n- 对于票价中包含但未使用的服务，当前 FAQ 表述为不予退款。", "risk_level": "medium", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__006", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "不同票价类型的退款差异", "chunk_text": "待人工确认：\n\n- 每个票价类型的具体退款比例。\n- 取消费计算方式。\n- 附加服务退款规则是否按航线、渠道或地区变化。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__007", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "航司取消航班", "chunk_text": "如果航司取消航班，旅客可能有资格获得全额退款或改订其他航班。\n\n待人工确认：\n\n- 恶劣天气、政治动荡等特殊情况是否属于航司免责场景。\n- 不同司法辖区下的补偿规则。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__008", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "退款货币", "chunk_text": "退款通常以机票发行货币进行。\n\n改签相关费用通常使用原始出发国家或起始点的货币计算。", "risk_level": "medium", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["refund", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__009", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "发票支付场景下的退款", "chunk_text": "如果通过按发票支付方式购买机票，取消后的退款或账单调整取决于付款状态：\n\n- 如果发票已支付，退款通常通过银行转账处理。\n- 如果付款期限未结束且发票未支付或仅部分支付，支付合作方可能发送新的个人发票，包含新金额和新付款期限。\n- 如果付款期限已结束且仍有未支付或部分支付款项，可能产生月度发票和额外费用。", "risk_level": "medium", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "invoice", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__010", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "人工处理场景", "chunk_text": "以下情况应升级人工处理：\n\n- 旅客要求确认具体退款金额。\n- 涉及不同国家/地区监管规则。\n- 票价类型无法识别。\n- 旅客通过旅行社、团体渠道或第三方渠道购买。\n- 航班取消原因涉及天气、政治、安全或不可抗力。\n- 用户对退款时效、退款方式或扣费金额提出争议。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "refund_policy__011", "policy_id": "refund_policy", "title": "取消与退款政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "refund", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/refund_policy.md", "section_title": "Agent 回答边界", "chunk_text": "在退款规则没有明确计算结果时，Agent 应使用审慎表达：\n\n- 可以说明一般规则。\n- 可以提示可能产生费用。\n- 不应承诺具体退款金额。\n- 不应承诺免费取消，除非政策和订单数据均明确支持。", "risk_level": "medium", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "invoice_policy__001", "policy_id": "invoice_policy", "title": "发票与电子机票确认政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "invoice", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/invoice_policy.md", "section_title": "适用范围", "chunk_text": "本政策用于回答旅客关于电子机票确认、发票申请、补开发票、特殊国家发票要求等问题。", "risk_level": "medium", "allowed_action": ["invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "invoice_policy__002", "policy_id": "invoice_policy", "title": "发票与电子机票确认政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "invoice", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/invoice_policy.md", "section_title": "电子机票确认作为发票", "chunk_text": "在多数国家和地区，包括瑞士，电子机票确认可作为收据使用，通常可用于费用报销和纳税申报。\n\n旅客可以在个人资料的预订页面中，通过电子文件或乘客收据相关入口订购电子机票确认。", "risk_level": "medium", "allowed_action": ["booking", "invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "invoice_policy__003", "policy_id": "invoice_policy", "title": "发票与电子机票确认政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "invoice", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/invoice_policy.md", "section_title": "补开发票或确认单", "chunk_text": "当前 FAQ 中存在两个不同口径：\n\n- 一处写明：机票或文件完全使用后的 100 天内，可免费发送新的预订确认；超过 100 天后，每笔交易收取 30 瑞士法郎，最多五张电子机票确认。\n- 另一处写明：机票或文件完全使用后的 90 天内，可免费发送新的预订确认；超过 90 天后，每张确认收取 30 瑞士法郎，最多五张电子机票确认。", "risk_level": "medium", "allowed_action": ["booking", "invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "invoice_policy__004", "policy_id": "invoice_policy", "title": "发票与电子机票确认政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "invoice", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/invoice_policy.md", "section_title": "补开发票或确认单", "chunk_text": "待人工确认：\n\n- 免费补发期限到底是 90 天还是 100 天。\n- 费用单位是“每笔交易”还是“每张确认”。\n- 最多五张电子机票确认是否适用于所有地区和渠道。\n\n在确认前，Agent 应回答为：系统资料存在 90 天和 100 天两个口径，建议转人工确认具体可补发期限和费用。", "risk_level": "high", "allowed_action": ["invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "invoice_policy__005", "policy_id": "invoice_policy", "title": "发票与电子机票确认政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "invoice", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/invoice_policy.md", "section_title": "特殊国家发票", "chunk_text": "对于从以下国家出发的航班，可能可以应要求开具特殊发票：\n\n- 希腊。\n- 印度。\n- 意大利。\n- 西班牙。\n\n如果电子机票上的信息不足以满足当地要求，旅客可以请求特殊发票。", "risk_level": "medium", "allowed_action": ["invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "invoice_policy__006", "policy_id": "invoice_policy", "title": "发票与电子机票确认政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "invoice", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/invoice_policy.md", "section_title": "发票相关人工处理场景", "chunk_text": "以下情况建议升级人工处理：\n\n- 旅客要求开具特殊国家发票。\n- 旅客需要公司抬头或特殊税务字段。\n- 超过免费补发期限。\n- 用户对 90 天/100 天规则、费用或数量限制提出确认。\n- 原订单来自第三方渠道或旅行社。", "risk_level": "high", "allowed_action": ["invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "invoice_policy__007", "policy_id": "invoice_policy", "title": "发票与电子机票确认政策", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "invoice", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": true, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/invoice_policy.md", "section_title": "Agent 回答边界", "chunk_text": "Agent 可以解释电子机票确认通常可作为收据或发票使用，但不应替代税务建议。\n\n如果旅客询问是否满足特定国家或公司财务要求，应建议联系人工客服或财务支持。", "risk_level": "medium", "allowed_action": ["invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__001", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "适用范围", "chunk_text": "本政策用于回答旅客关于信用卡安全码、3-D Secure、按发票支付、货币转换支付和退款货币的问题。", "allowed_action": ["invoice", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__002", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "信用卡安全码", "chunk_text": "为了提高在线支付安全性，系统会要求旅客输入信用卡或借记卡安全码，以检查卡信息有效性。\n\n常见卡组织安全码位置：\n\n- 美国运通：安全码通常是卡正面信用卡号码上方的 4 位数字。\n- 万事达卡：安全码通常是卡背面签名栏处的 3 位数字。\n- Visa：安全码通常是卡背面签名栏处的 3 位数字。\n- 大来卡：安全码通常是卡背面签名栏处的 3 位数字。\n- JCB：安全码通常是卡背面签名栏处的 3 位数字。\n- 中国银联信用卡：安全码通常位于卡背面签名栏中。"}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__003", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "支付安全标准", "chunk_text": "支付流程遵循支付卡行业数据安全标准，用于规范支付数据的存储、传输和处理。\n\n信用卡和借记卡交易相关支付数据应按安全标准进行加密处理。"}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__004", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "3-D Secure", "chunk_text": "在欧盟经济区发行的信用卡和借记卡，可能需要进行 3-D Secure 认证。\n\n3-D Secure 是一个额外认证步骤，用于提升支付安全并降低欺诈风险。\n\n如果旅客尚未注册，通常需要通过发卡银行的网站完成注册。认证流程由发卡银行决定。\n\n如果交易适用 3-D Secure，旅客可能会被重定向到银行网站完成认证。"}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__005", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "3-D Secure", "chunk_text": "关于 3-D Secure 注册或认证失败的问题，旅客应联系发卡银行或卡片发行机构。"}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__006", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "按发票支付", "chunk_text": "按发票支付通常要求：\n\n- 旅客年满 18 岁。\n- 旅客是瑞士或列支敦士登居民。\n- 支付选项通常仅适用于从瑞士出发的航班。\n\n该支付方式可能需要 ID 扫描和自拍比对，以防止欺诈和身份盗用。\n\n如果 ID 扫描失败，旅客应确保照片清晰、曝光良好、避免反光，不遮挡文件，并使用近期个人照片。文件未被识别时，可以重复扫描。", "allowed_action": ["invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__007", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "按发票支付", "chunk_text": "按发票支付授权失败可能与信用状况、信息矛盾、未支付发票等原因有关。", "allowed_action": ["invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__008", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "POWERPAY 发票", "chunk_text": "按发票支付场景下，个人发票通常会在约 24 至 48 小时后通过电子邮件发送。\n\n如果个人发票按时支付，通常不会产生额外费用。\n\n如果未按时支付，未付款项可能汇总为月度账户对账单。月度发票可能产生费用。\n\n付款期限和提醒费用：\n\n- 个人发票通常需在收到电子邮件后 15 天内支付。\n- 月度发票付款截止日期通常为月底。\n- 月度发票逾期可能产生提醒费用。", "allowed_action": ["invoice"]}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__009", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "货币转换支付", "chunk_text": "通过 swiss.com 预订时，旅客可能可以选择以不同货币支付。\n\n货币转换支付的特点：\n\n- 旅客可以决定以哪种货币向信用卡收费。\n- 系统显示每日汇率，并保证本次支付使用该汇率。\n- 如果以信用卡本币支付，可能避免部分外币交易费用。\n\n该服务通常不适用于：", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__010", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "货币转换支付", "chunk_text": "- 更改航班。\n- 后续升级。\n- 附加服务，例如额外行李。\n- 通过不同预订渠道购买的机票。\n\n退款通常以机票发行货币进行。", "allowed_action": ["booking", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "payment_policy__011", "policy_id": "payment_policy", "title": "支付与信用卡安全政策", "service": "payment", "policy_type": "payment", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/payment_policy.md", "section_title": "人工处理场景", "chunk_text": "以下情况建议升级人工处理：\n\n- 支付授权失败且用户无法判断原因。\n- 3-D Secure 认证多次失败。\n- 发票支付状态、提醒费用或退款金额存在争议。\n- 用户要求更改付款人、公司地址或账单信息。\n- 涉及退款币种、汇率或银行额外费用争议。", "risk_level": "high", "allowed_action": ["invoice", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__001", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "适用范围", "chunk_text": "本政策用于回答旅客关于舱位代码、欧洲票价概念、行李规则、升级和附加服务的问题。"}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__002", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "舱位类型", "chunk_text": "原始 FAQ 中列出以下舱位代码：\n\n- 经济舱：`B`、`E`、`G`、`H`、`K`、`L`、`M`、`Q`、`S`、`T`、`U`、`V`、`W`、`Y`\n- 商务舱：`C`、`D`、`J`、`P`、`Z`\n- 头等舱：`A`、`F`"}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__003", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "舱位类型", "chunk_text": "这些字母用于表示不同服务等级中的不同价格类别。\n\n旅客可以在预订过程中查看已预订机票的票价条件。票价条件可能以英文显示。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__004", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "欧洲票价概念", "chunk_text": "只要经济舱仍有座位，经济舱相关票价类型通常会在每个可用预订舱位中提供。\n\n经济经典、经济灵活和商务舱票价可以在代码共享航班上预订。\n\n经济轻便票价通常只能预订由瑞士航空运营的航班。由于技术原因，部分代码共享航班可能无法预订座位。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__005", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "团体票价", "chunk_text": "团体预订在机票出票前通常可以免费更改为任何票价选项，前提是相同价格仍然可用。\n\n因此，经济灵活票价对团体可能没有额外好处，当前 FAQ 表示不提供给团体。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__006", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "附加服务", "chunk_text": "附加选项包括提前座位预订、额外行李等。\n\n对于经济轻便票价，附加选项通常不能随票价一起改签，因为票价本身无法更改。\n\n对于经济经典票价，附加选项通常只能在相同预订中预订。", "allowed_action": ["booking", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__007", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "升级", "chunk_text": "旅客如果预订经济轻便、经济经典或经济灵活票价，通常可以预订包含商务舱部分服务的商务舱升级。\n\n升级通常可以通过 swiss.com 或服务中心办理。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__008", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "状态客户和会员", "chunk_text": "状态客户，例如 HON Circle 会员、参议员、常旅客，在选择票价时应注意：\n\n- 经济轻便票价不包括免费提前座位预订。\n- 经济轻便票价不包括额外行李，例如高尔夫设备。\n- 其他状态福利，例如休息室访问，通常保持不变。\n\n瑞士高尔夫旅行者俱乐部会员在选择经济轻便票价时，应注意不能免费携带高尔夫行李。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__009", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "里程积分", "chunk_text": "里程积分数量通常由预订舱位决定。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__010", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "行李规则", "chunk_text": "经济轻便票价中的第一件行李可以通过以下渠道购买：\n\n- 旅行社。\n- swiss.com，通常起飞前最多 6 小时。\n- 瑞士航空服务中心，通常起飞前最多 24 小时。\n- 机场。\n\n机场价格通常高于提前购买价格，并且每段航线均需支付费用。"}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__011", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "行李规则", "chunk_text": "第一件行李只能与经济轻便票价一起购买，费用通常低于额外行李。\n\n通过 swiss.com 最多可购买两件额外行李。\n\n通过旅行社预订时，通常最多可以购买一件第一件行李加一件额外行李。\n\n通过服务中心预订时，可购买额外行李数量可能没有限制。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__012", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "同日改签到较早航班", "chunk_text": "经济灵活和商务灵活票价可能支持同一天改签到较早航班。\n\n该服务通常适用于：\n\n- 出发当天办理。\n- 通过 lufthansa.com、汉莎航空应用程序、机场登机机或登机柜台办理。\n- 直飞航班。\n\n该服务通常不支持更改航线或航空公司。", "allowed_action": ["ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "fare_rules__013", "policy_id": "fare_rules", "title": "票价、舱位、行李与升级规则", "service": "flight", "policy_type": "fare_rules", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/fare_rules.md", "section_title": "人工处理场景", "chunk_text": "以下情况建议升级人工处理：\n\n- 旅客询问具体票价金额、费用差额或退款金额。\n- 涉及代码共享航班座位预订。\n- 涉及状态客户、会员权益或高尔夫行李权益争议。\n- 涉及团体预订。\n- 涉及附加服务退款或转移。", "risk_level": "high", "allowed_action": ["booking", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__001", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "适用范围", "chunk_text": "本政策用于回答旅客关于个人资料中的预订展示、App 与桌面功能差异、第三方预订和团体预订的问题。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__002", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "个人资料中的预订展示", "chunk_text": "2021 年 10 月 28 日之前通过 swiss.com 个人资料或瑞士航空应用程序进行的预订，可能不再显示在个人资料中。\n\n旅客可以根据需要再次添加这些预订。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__003", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "第三方预订展示", "chunk_text": "如果旅客想将朋友、家人等第三方预订添加到个人资料中，应优先使用智能手机。\n\n通过桌面电脑、笔记本电脑或平板电脑，通常只能添加与个人资料所有者本人相关的联合预订。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__004", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "票价舱位和座位图展示", "chunk_text": "通过桌面电脑、笔记本电脑和平板电脑，旅客通常可以在航班结果中直接查看：\n\n- 票价的预订舱位信息。\n- 航班座位图。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__005", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "升级安排入口", "chunk_text": "通过桌面电脑、笔记本电脑和平板电脑，旅客通常可以在完成预订后，通过个人资料中的“我的预订”“编辑预订”“为此航班预订升级”等入口安排升级。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__006", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "团体预订", "chunk_text": "超过九名乘客的预订应使用团体预订表格处理。\n\n团体预订相关改签、取消、费用和乘客变更通常需要人工处理。", "risk_level": "high", "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__007", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "App 与桌面功能差异", "chunk_text": "信用卡数据的保存取决于使用设备。\n\n通过桌面电脑、笔记本电脑或平板电脑保存到个人资料中的信用卡数据，可能无法在智能手机上使用；反之亦然。\n\n部分功能和服务可能暂时只支持桌面电脑、笔记本电脑和平板电脑，包括：\n\n- 兑换代金券。\n- 使用促销代码。\n- 预订多程航班。\n- 进行改签。", "allowed_action": ["booking", "ticket_change"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__008", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "汉莎航空集团航班", "chunk_text": "旅客可以选择汉莎航空集团航空公司提供的所有航班。具体可预订范围以系统结果为准。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__009", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "客服支持", "chunk_text": "如果旅客遇到个人资料、设备差异、第三方预订、团体预订或升级入口问题，应联系客户支持。", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "booking_platform_policy__010", "policy_id": "booking_platform_policy", "title": "预订平台与个人资料规则", "service": "booking", "policy_type": "platform", "source": "order_faq.md", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/booking_platform_policy.md", "section_title": "人工处理场景", "chunk_text": "以下情况建议升级人工处理：\n\n- 超过九人的团体预订。\n- 第三方预订无法添加到个人资料。\n- App 和桌面显示结果不一致。\n- 旅客无法查看历史预订。\n- 涉及套餐、旅行社或企业客户预订。", "risk_level": "high", "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "hotel_policy__001", "policy_id": "hotel_policy", "title": "酒店预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "hotel", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/hotel_policy.md", "section_title": "适用范围", "chunk_text": "本政策为 V1 模拟业务政策，用于支持旅行客服 Agent 回答酒店查询、预订、修改和取消相关问题。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel"]}
{"chunk_id": "hotel_policy__002", "policy_id": "hotel_policy", "title": "酒店预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "hotel", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/hotel_policy.md", "section_title": "酒店预订", "chunk_text": "旅客可以根据城市、酒店名称或价格层级查询可选酒店。\n\n预订成功后，系统应记录酒店 ID、旅客 ID、入住日期、退房日期和预订状态。\n\n当前 demo 数据仅以 `booked` 字段标记预订状态，不能代表真实库存或真实用户订单。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "hotel_policy__003", "policy_id": "hotel_policy", "title": "酒店预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "hotel", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/hotel_policy.md", "section_title": "取消规则", "chunk_text": "酒店预订是否可取消取决于酒店房价规则和取消时间。\n\nV1 默认规则：\n\n- 入住日前 24 小时之前取消，通常可免费取消。\n- 入住日前 24 小时内取消，可能产生一晚房费或固定取消费。\n- 已入住或超过入住日期后取消，通常不可自动退款。\n\n具体取消费用和退款金额应以订单详情和酒店确认规则为准。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "hotel_policy__004", "policy_id": "hotel_policy", "title": "酒店预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "hotel", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/hotel_policy.md", "section_title": "入住和退房日期修改", "chunk_text": "旅客可以申请修改入住日期或退房日期。\n\nV1 默认规则：\n\n- 修改必须在入住前完成。\n- 修改后的日期必须符合酒店可售库存。\n- 修改可能导致价格变化。\n- 如果修改失败，应保留原预订，除非旅客确认取消。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel"]}
{"chunk_id": "hotel_policy__005", "policy_id": "hotel_policy", "title": "酒店预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "hotel", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/hotel_policy.md", "section_title": "部分退款", "chunk_text": "部分退款仅在以下场景可考虑：\n\n- 提前退房且酒店确认可退。\n- 因航班取消或不可抗力导致无法入住。\n- 酒店无法履约，例如无法提供已确认房型。\n\n部分退款金额需要人工确认。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "hotel_policy__006", "policy_id": "hotel_policy", "title": "酒店预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "hotel", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/hotel_policy.md", "section_title": "超时未入住", "chunk_text": "如果旅客未按预订日期入住，酒店可能将订单标记为 no-show。\n\nno-show 订单通常不支持自动退款。\n\n如果旅客因航班延误、取消或紧急情况无法入住，应升级人工处理。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "hotel_policy__007", "policy_id": "hotel_policy", "title": "酒店预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "hotel", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/hotel_policy.md", "section_title": "人工处理场景", "chunk_text": "以下情况应升级人工处理：\n\n- 旅客要求确认具体退款金额。\n- 入住日当天取消或修改。\n- 已入住后要求退款。\n- 酒店无法确认库存。\n- 旅客要求特殊房型、无障碍设施、加床、携带宠物或多人入住。\n- 航班异常导致无法按时入住。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "hotel_policy__008", "policy_id": "hotel_policy", "title": "酒店预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "hotel", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/hotel_policy.md", "section_title": "Agent 回答边界", "chunk_text": "Agent 可以说明一般规则和发起查询、预订、修改或取消流程。\n\n在没有酒店确认规则和订单价格时，Agent 不应承诺具体退款金额。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "car_rental_policy__001", "policy_id": "car_rental_policy", "title": "租车预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "car_rental", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/car_rental_policy.md", "section_title": "适用范围", "chunk_text": "本政策为 V1 模拟业务政策，用于支持旅行客服 Agent 回答租车查询、预订、修改和取消相关问题。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel"]}
{"chunk_id": "car_rental_policy__002", "policy_id": "car_rental_policy", "title": "租车预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "car_rental", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/car_rental_policy.md", "section_title": "租车预订", "chunk_text": "旅客可以根据城市、租车公司或车型/价格层级查询租车服务。\n\n预订时应确认：\n\n- 取车城市。\n- 取车日期。\n- 还车日期。\n- 租车公司。\n- 车型或价格层级。\n\n当前 demo 数据仅以 `booked` 字段标记预订状态，不能代表真实车辆库存或真实用户订单。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "car_rental_policy__003", "policy_id": "car_rental_policy", "title": "租车预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "car_rental", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/car_rental_policy.md", "section_title": "起租前取消", "chunk_text": "V1 默认规则：\n\n- 起租前 24 小时之前取消，通常可免费取消。\n- 起租前 24 小时内取消，可能产生取消费。\n- 未按时取车可能被视为 no-show，通常不支持自动退款。\n\n具体费用以租车公司确认规则为准。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "car_rental_policy__004", "policy_id": "car_rental_policy", "title": "租车预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "car_rental", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/car_rental_policy.md", "section_title": "起租后修改", "chunk_text": "起租后修改通常需要人工处理。\n\n可能涉及：\n\n- 延长租期。\n- 提前还车。\n- 更换车型。\n- 更换还车地点。\n- 增加驾驶人。\n\n这些场景通常会影响价格、保险和责任划分。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true}
{"chunk_id": "car_rental_policy__005", "policy_id": "car_rental_policy", "title": "租车预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "car_rental", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/car_rental_policy.md", "section_title": "保险和责任说明", "chunk_text": "V1 简化规则：\n\n- 租车订单可能包含基础保险，具体保障范围以租车公司条款为准。\n- 车辆损坏、违章、超时还车、燃油差异等费用可能由旅客承担。\n- Agent 不应解释具体保险赔付金额。"}
{"chunk_id": "car_rental_policy__006", "policy_id": "car_rental_policy", "title": "租车预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "car_rental", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/car_rental_policy.md", "section_title": "证件要求", "chunk_text": "旅客取车时通常需要提供：\n\n- 有效驾驶证。\n- 有效身份证件或护照。\n- 用于押金或担保的信用卡。\n\n国际租车可能需要国际驾照或翻译件。"}
{"chunk_id": "car_rental_policy__007", "policy_id": "car_rental_policy", "title": "租车预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "car_rental", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/car_rental_policy.md", "section_title": "人工处理场景", "chunk_text": "以下情况应升级人工处理：\n\n- 起租后修改或取消。\n- 旅客无法提供证件。\n- 涉及事故、违章、车辆损坏或保险理赔。\n- 异地还车。\n- 增加驾驶人。\n- 租车公司无法确认库存。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel"]}
{"chunk_id": "car_rental_policy__008", "policy_id": "car_rental_policy", "title": "租车预订、修改与取消政策", "service": "car_rental", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/car_rental_policy.md", "section_title": "Agent 回答边界", "chunk_text": "Agent 可以查询和发起预订、修改、取消流程。\n\n在未获得租车公司确认前，Agent 不应承诺具体车辆、押金金额、保险赔付或退款金额。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "excursion_policy__001", "policy_id": "excursion_policy", "title": "景点与行程推荐预订政策", "service": "excursion", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/excursion_policy.md", "section_title": "适用范围", "chunk_text": "本政策为 V1 模拟业务政策，用于支持旅行客服 Agent 回答景点、当地体验、行程推荐的查询、预订、改期和取消问题。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel"]}
{"chunk_id": "excursion_policy__002", "policy_id": "excursion_policy", "title": "景点与行程推荐预订政策", "service": "excursion", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/excursion_policy.md", "section_title": "查询与预订", "chunk_text": "旅客可以根据城市、推荐名称或关键词查询景点和行程推荐。\n\n预订前应确认：\n\n- 推荐项目名称。\n- 城市或集合地点。\n- 活动日期和时间。\n- 参与人数。\n- 是否存在年龄、身体状况、天气或语言限制。\n\n当前 demo 数据仅以 `booked` 字段标记预订状态，不能代表真实活动名额或真实用户订单。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking"]}
{"chunk_id": "excursion_policy__003", "policy_id": "excursion_policy", "title": "景点与行程推荐预订政策", "service": "excursion", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/excursion_policy.md", "section_title": "取消规则", "chunk_text": "V1 默认规则：\n\n- 活动开始前 24 小时之前取消，通常可免费取消。\n- 活动开始前 24 小时内取消，可能产生取消费。\n- 活动开始后或旅客未到场，通常不支持自动退款。\n\n具体退款金额以活动供应商规则为准。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "excursion_policy__004", "policy_id": "excursion_policy", "title": "景点与行程推荐预订政策", "service": "excursion", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/excursion_policy.md", "section_title": "改期规则", "chunk_text": "旅客可以申请活动改期。\n\nV1 默认规则：\n\n- 改期必须在活动开始前提出。\n- 改期是否成功取决于活动名额和供应商确认。\n- 改期可能产生价格差异。\n- 如果改期失败，应保留原预订，除非旅客确认取消。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel"]}
{"chunk_id": "excursion_policy__005", "policy_id": "excursion_policy", "title": "景点与行程推荐预订政策", "service": "excursion", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/excursion_policy.md", "section_title": "退款规则", "chunk_text": "以下场景可能支持退款或部分退款：\n\n- 活动供应商取消活动。\n- 因恶劣天气导致活动无法进行。\n- 活动项目无法按原确认内容提供。\n- 旅客在免费取消时间前取消。\n\n以下场景通常不支持自动退款：\n\n- 活动已开始。\n- 旅客未到场。\n- 旅客未满足证件、年龄、健康或安全要求。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "excursion_policy__006", "policy_id": "excursion_policy", "title": "景点与行程推荐预订政策", "service": "excursion", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/excursion_policy.md", "section_title": "人工处理场景", "chunk_text": "以下情况应升级人工处理：\n\n- 活动开始后退款。\n- 天气、安全或供应商取消问题。\n- 多人订单部分取消。\n- 涉及儿童、老人、行动不便旅客或特殊健康要求。\n- 用户对活动体验提出投诉。\n- 需要确认具体退款金额。", "risk_level": "high", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["cancel", "refund"]}
{"chunk_id": "excursion_policy__007", "policy_id": "excursion_policy", "title": "景点与行程推荐预订政策", "service": "excursion", "policy_type": "booking_policy", "source": "internal_mock_policy", "review_status": "draft", "requires_human_review": false, "file_path": "kb/raw/policy/excursion_policy.md", "section_title": "Agent 回答边界", "chunk_text": "Agent 可以推荐项目、查询候选活动，并发起预订、改期或取消流程。\n\n在没有供应商确认前，Agent 不应承诺活动名额、退款金额或特殊安排一定可执行。", "requires_confirmation": true, "allowed_action": ["booking", "cancel", "refund"]}
